  <summary date="2023-01-27T03:07:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Clean Water SRF Parity Act

This bill expands the state revolving fund established under the Clean Water Act, including by allowing low-interest loans to be given to privately owned treatment works to address wastewater. Currently, loans are given to wastewater systems that are publicly owned.</summary>
